    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
      <h1>Produktionskontrol af nytårsfyrværkeri</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
        
                  
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

Vi har samlet en række informationer, som man skal være opmærksomme på i forbindelse med produktionskontrol af konsumfyrværkeri. 
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                </p>
      </summary>
      <hr>

          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Hvorfor skal vi lave produktionskontrol?</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det er en betingelse for jeres virksomhedsgodkendelse, at I har et kvalitetsstyringssystem, der omfatter produktionskontrol. I skal vedligeholde og anvende kvalitetsstyringssystemet og udføre den forventede produktionskontrol.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I skal med kontrollen sikre, at alle producerede og mærkede artikler svarer til den typegodkendte model.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Hvilken fabrikant og testinstans skal vi vælge?</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I bør vælge en fabrikant, hvis kvalitetsstyringssystem, I har gennemgået og fundet tilfredsstillende.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I bør vælge en uafhængig testinstans med forstand på testning af fyrværkeri. Eller I kan vælge selv at være til stede under udførelsen af produktionskontrollen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvordan skal vi lave produktionskontrollen?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I skal udføre produktionskontrollen og lave en testrapport, så kravene i fyrværkeristandarderne (DS/EN 14035-serien) er opfyldt. I kan tage udgangspunkt i annex B i standardserien.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Bemærk, at det skal tjekkes, om mærkningen på artiklerne eller emballagen er med den korrekte tekst. Det kan være vanskeligt for en kinesisk testinstans.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I skal kontrollere, om det producerede nytårsfyrværkeri svarer til det typegodkendte. Som minimum bør 3 artikler pr. produceret batch udtages til vejning af NEM.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Er det en god idé at udvide kontrollen?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det er en god idé at lave en bredere produktionskontrol.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I kan f.eks. teste artiklernes indhold af forbudte stoffer, spredningssats m.m.. Ved at udvide kontrollen kan I bedre sikre jer, at alle producerede og mærkede artikler er i overensstemmelse med den typegodkendte model.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I kan vælge at gentage testen af særligt kritiske forhold efter modtagelse af artiklen i Danmark.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad er en batch?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

En batch er en portion af en vare, der masseproduceres over en fastsat periode. De producerede batches bliver typisk nummeret fortløbende, så sporbarheden kan opretholdes (produktionsdato, råvarer mv.).<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

Det er en god idé at skrive batchnummeret (Lot nr.) på testrapporten.<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Dermed kan I senere dokumentere, at en given batch er testet og fundet i overensstemmelse med den typegodkendte model.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Er der krav til udstyret?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p> Det anvendte udstyr skal være af samme kvalitet som det specificerede udstyr i fyrværkeristandarderne (DS/EN 14035-serien).</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Skal vi teste emballagen?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I skal teste en emballage, hvis den har en sikkerhedsfunktion. Dvs. hvis den fungerer som luntebeskyttelse, eller hvis mærkningen står på den.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I skal udtage det antal af emballager til kontrol som fremgår af B.3 i annex B i fyrværkeristandarderne. Antallet af emballager, som skal udtages til kontrol, afhænger af antallet af producerede emballager i en batch. Ligesom for selve fyrværkeriartiklerne.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Testresultaterne for emballagen skal stå i testrapporten. Testresultaterne kan også være et supplement til testrapporten, hvis det er en emballage, som indeholder flere forskellige artikler.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Skal vi dokumentere produktionskontrollen?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ja, I skal dokumentere, at der er lavet produktionskontrol ved for eksempel at lave en testrapport.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Testrapporten skal mindst indeholde de punkter, der er markeret med * i A.7 (typetestrapporten). I B.5 i annex B kan I se de specifikke krav til batchtestrapporten.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Sprog og opbevaring af dokumentation for produktionskontrol</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Jeres dokumentation bør være på dansk eller engelsk.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I skal kunne vise os jeres dokumentation med få dages varsel. Dokumentationen bør opbevares på jeres hovedkontor i Danmark.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Elektronisk dokumentation er tilstrækkelig. Dokumenterne skal opbevares sådan, at der ikke kan rettes i dem.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
          
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/override/templates/line/faq_item.tpl) -->
<div class="faq-item">
  <div class="question hover">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad kan vi selv gøre for at tjekke testrapporten?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
</div>
  <div class="answer">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p> I kan blandt andet tjekke, at følgende fremgår: </p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Fabrikantens navn og produktionsperioden for artiklen </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Testfirmaets navn og testtidspunktet </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Antallet af artikler i batchen samt batchens nummer </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Antallet af testede artikler og emballager </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Testrapporten mindst indeholder de punkter, der er markeret med * i A.7 (typetestrapporten i standardserien DS/EN 14035) </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Kun testresultater relevante for artiklens kategori </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>De anvendte acceptkriterier for hver test. Dvs. kriteriet for at en artikel består eller ikke består testen </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Test af hver type element i et batteri </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>Dokumentation for undersøgelser af artiklens overensstemmelse med det typegodkendte, f.eks. NEM-vejninger </li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>I bør overveje, om testrapporten er troværdig, hvis der aldrig konstateres afvigelser blandt de testede artikler. </p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
